ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectCanada Lands Company Limited ** Corporate Plan ** 2009-10 to 2013-14 amendment
PrecisOrder approving the amendment to the CORPORATE PLAN of CANADA LANDS COMPANY LIMITED for the 2009-10 to 2013-14 planning period, to authorize its subsidiary, Canada Lands Company CLC Limited (CLC), to proceed with changes to its borrowing plan for the 2009-2010 planning period in support of ongoing operations of the Metro Toronto Convention Centre Complex (MTCCC).
